NAME
    Module::Build::Pluggable::DistTestLibCoreOnly - (EXPERIMENTAL) run
    disttest with local lib

SYNOPSIS
        use Module::Build::Pluggable qw(
            DistTestLibCoreOnly
        );

DESCRIPTION
    Run disttest with depended modules wrote in deps only.

    THIS IS A DEVELOPMENT RELEASE. API MAY CHANGE WITHOUT NOTICE.

    This plugin installs depended modules to " _local_lib/ " by " cpanm -L
    _local_lib/ ". And run the test cases with the libraries only.

